The authorities of the Russian Federation have recently markedly stepped up their policy in the Libyan direction, and with visits to Moscow participated delegations of the opposing Libyan sides.
The head of the Russian contact group on intra-Libyan settlement with the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Russian Federation and the State Duma, the assistant of the head of the Chechen Republic Lev Dengov told “Y” what goals Moscow is pursuing in this region and who is betting on.
Almost nothing is known about the Libyan contact group you are heading.
Here, let's say, the contact group in Ukraine - everyone knows about it.
Here's the secret curtain.
What exactly do you do, what goals do you pursue?
The contact group was established on the initiative of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Russian Federation and the State Duma.
